			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">The Audacious Scheme to Reroute India’s Water</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Scientists are watching with concern as India prepares to break ground on a long-delayed plan to connect the country’s rivers.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/sushmita-pathak/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Sushmita Pathak</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						June 20, 2024 | 1,000 words, about 5 minutes
					</aside>

					
				</header>

				
